  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8adeb66ea48d6884c9ae1c35b5ca9e1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Union 3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueScript
  defaultPanelType: 0
  nextConversation: {fileID: 0}
  changeSceneOnEnd: 0
  sceneToLoadOnEnd: 
  conversationLines:
  - speaker: 
    text: "Ambos parec\xEDan a punto de volver a pelearse, pero una voz mas suave
      los interrumpi\xF3.\r\n"
    showImage: 0
    characterImage: {fileID: 0}
    imagePosition: 0
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 1
    newBackground: {fileID: -2791861649169482472, guid: 8dc6b7c72819b06448cb61cca7c92373, type: 3}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: ???
    text: "Disculpen\u2026 \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500el muchacho rubio de ropas
      pueblerinos se acerc\xF3 lentamente, sosteniendo una caja con vendas y trozos
      de pan envueltos con tela, probablemente se mi edad, aunque por su expresi\xF3n
      cansada se ve\xEDa unos a\xF1os mayor\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500. La se\xF1ora
      Louise esta  mejor.\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: -5748912362787912128, guid: 830407863e207d5498f6665558403051, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Jean Dubois
    text: "Ah, Gabriel quiere salvar Francia el solo \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500murmur\xF3
      divertido Jean.\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: 2433035244665607080, guid: 48ccfea1a6bfbef488cf017275230f1d, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Gabriel
    text: "Solo intento ayudar \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500su mirada baj\xF3 t\xEDmidamente
      al suelo, su voz era baja, pero segura, posiblemente muy preocupado por las
      personas.\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: 2881689380543344907, guid: ae8bc8aa98bc76340ae19b746eeab1a0, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Jules Laurent
    text: "El es Gabriel Bernard, es el hijo del representante del pueblo. Seguro
      ya lo has visto, su padre esta enfermo y \xE9l anda ocupado su lugar \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500explic\xF3
      Jules con calma\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500. Es t\xEDmido, a diferencia de
      Jean, trata de no molestarlo.\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: 6132321653257676300, guid: 0e351293a5e9d1945b919c54ad4bee83, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Gabriel Bernant
    text: "Escuch\xE9 lo que hiciste en el pueblo \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500solt\xF3
      t\xEDmidamente Gabriel\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500. Unos se\xF1ores dijeron
      que estuviste para ellos luego de que un guardia los atacara.\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: -4189773919495433949, guid: 190fd7fb538f0484ca3779896358558f, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: 
    text: "Que vergonzoso era saber que hab\xEDan m\xE1s personas enteradas, Elodie
      apoy\xF3 una mano en mi hombro al verme tan tenso."
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: 168661227485434523, guid: 17bfadfbd598e5e4b8abcaf37a53538d, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 1
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Jean Dubois
    text: "\xBFVes? Ya eres popular entre nosotros, \xA1necesitamos la valent\xEDa
      de todas las personas posibles! Gente que quiera acabar con este sistema y
      haga lo que sea para conseguirlo. \xBFNo te gustar\xEDa unirte?\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: -4988242933721425723, guid: 46bce7f00b4eee246a1da01a66cbb2d1, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Francois
    text: Yo...
    showImage: 0
    characterImage: {fileID: 0}
    imagePosition: 0
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: 
    text: "Trat\xE9 de hablar, pero fui interrumpido por Jules, que se ve\xEDa molesto
      ante eso."
    showImage: 0
    characterImage: {fileID: 0}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 1
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Jules Laurent
    text: "Deja de tratar de llevarte a m\xE1s gente a tu ideas tan radicales, Fran\xE7ois,
      te quiero dar la posibilidad de unirte a nosotros, buscamos soluciones menos
      extremistas, sin necesidad de violencia. \r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: 6132321653257676300, guid: 0e351293a5e9d1945b919c54ad4bee83, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: Gabriel Bernart
    text: "Nos vendr\xEDa bien gente que ayude con el pueblo\u2026 nos estamos muriendo
      de hambre, alguien que nos ayude a administrar todo vendr\xEDa bien.\r\n"
    showImage: 1
    characterImage: {fileID: 6132321653257676300, guid: 0e351293a5e9d1945b919c54ad4bee83, type: 3}
    imagePosition: 2
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 0
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
    choices: []
  - speaker: 
    text: "Los tres me miraron, que situaci\xF3n tan incomoda, \xBFa quien deb\xEDa
      elegir?\r\n"
    showImage: 0
    characterImage: {fileID: 0}
    imagePosition: 0
    characterImageSize: {x: 0, y: 0}
    panelType: 1
    newBackground: {fileID: 0}
    triggerShake: 0
    shakeDuration: 0
    shakeIntensity: 0
    choicePanelType: 0
